---
title: Korean Style BBQ Pork and Veg Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice and Pickled Carrot Ribbons
description: This delicious Korean Style BBQ Pork and Veg Stir-Fry has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_HF_Y23_R25_W35_UK_L15503-4_Main__1low-daab768a.jpg
